{"tid":855918,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【賽跑冠軍】港灣道男子衝出馬路 遭七人車猛撼重創","createTime":"2018-10-10T10:14:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T10:29:23.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c362d4fd1e98f90c42bbddec96e62fbdd20c6d66","tid":855918,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T10:14:23.000Z","msg":"灣仔發生交通意外，下午2時許，一名49歲男子於港灣道港灣道花園對開欲橫過馬路往對面的鷹君中心，惟他跑過兩條行車線後，剛巧另一邊方向的七人車駛至，司機收掣不及將其撞倒，他倒卧地上彈飛數米。傷者其後由救護車送往律敦治醫院搶救，警方正調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n目擊事件的讀者林先生表示，當時駕車途經上址停燈位，看見一名男子突然橫過港灣道馬路，但未有望清楚交通情況，「佢淨係望住右手邊嘅車，冇望對頭車嘅方向就衝咗出去」，詎料走至一半的時候被另一方向的七人車迎頭撞上。傷者被撞後躺卧地上陷入昏迷，沒有任何反應。林生稱，意外發生後，有熱心途人上前替傷者開遮擋雨。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181010/58778761\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181010%2F58778761&d=mbpCeGZ7F5pg7ap3sWC%2FOqMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=92675dc9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181010%2F58778761&h=a9b35475\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181010/58778761</a>"},{"pid":"e08baebeb88c2a06f0c9d8e381ace7a4727a682e","tid":855918,"uid":69213,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T10:14:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"23cfb1420860ca6aacadd52aeac27b9ca484cd9e","tid":855918,"uid":522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T10:24:33.000Z","msg":"累死司機"},{"pid":"75491ed76b26cfdaf6968d5dd75d4d8b89e8e1d2","tid":855918,"uid":99805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T10:26:48.000Z","msg":"果到日日都大把人咁樣過<br />\n阿叔都算樣衰"},{"pid":"db11f01035085a644dc24ff41be5bb5bd9a57183","tid":855918,"uid":38946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T10:28:48.000Z","msg":"真係抵撚死 果個位跨幾條線 d 車又急<br />\n死撚左去好過"},{"pid":"4104dde87ecfcccce592b1eeac7ca60b5a11a05e